.TP
.B Ctrl-G
Grab next DX spot from bandmap.
.
.TP
.B Ctrl-K
Keyboard (CW and RTTY).
.
.TP
.B Ctrl-P
Maximum Usable Frequency (MUF) display.
.
.TP
.B Ctrl-Q
XOFF (Linux terminal function).
