.B Alt-0 ... Alt-9
Send CW (Morse code) messages.
.
.TP
.B Alt-A
Cycle cluster window: NOCLUSTER \(-> CLUSTER \(-> BANDMAP \(-> ...
.
.TP
.B Alt-B
Band up.
.
.TP
.B Alt-C
Toggle display of checkwindow.
.
.TP
.B Alt-E
Enter QSO edit mode.
.
.TP
.B Alt-G
Grab first spot from bandmap which has the characters in the call input
